decs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/750660/extras/85586a97095288b3b7e1cc365c8565b6.mp4?t=1647867646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- At the beginning of the game each player has 8 pieces;<br><br>- Each player tries to knock the opponent's pieces off the board;<br><br>- The player, who successfully knocks out all the pieces of the opponent, is declared a winner!",
